#: ../index.rst:3
msgid "Welcome to Fabric's documentation!"
msgstr "欢迎访问 Fabric 中文文档"

#: ../index.rst:5
msgid ""
"This site covers Fabric's usage & API documentation. For basic info on what "
"Fabric is, including its public changelog & how the project is maintained, "
"please see `the main project website <http://fabfile.org>`_."
msgstr ""
"本站覆盖了 Fabric 的用法和 API 文档，包括变更历史和维护信息等 Fabric 基本信息"
"见 `Fabric 官方网站 <http://fabfile.org/>`_ 。"

#: ../index.rst:11
msgid "Tutorial"
msgstr "入门教程"

#: ../index.rst:13
msgid ""
"For new users, and/or for an overview of Fabric's basic functionality, "
"please see the :doc:`tutorial`. The rest of the documentation will assume "
"you're at least passingly familiar with the material contained within."
msgstr ""
"对于新用户，以及/或想大概了解 Fabric 基本功能的同学，请访问 :doc:`tutorial` 。"
"本文档的其它部分将假设你至少已经大概熟悉其中的内容。"

#: ../index.rst:26
msgid "Usage documentation"
msgstr "使用文档"

#: ../index.rst:28
msgid ""
"The following list contains all major sections of Fabric's prose (non-API) "
"documentation, which expands upon the concepts outlined in the "
":doc:`tutorial` and also covers advanced topics."
msgstr ""
"下面的列表包含了 Fabric （非 API 部分）文档的主要章节。这些内容对 :doc:`tutorial` "
"中提到的概念进行了扩展，同时还覆盖了一些高级主题。"

#: ../index.rst:42
msgid "API documentation"
msgstr "API 文档"

#: ../index.rst:44
msgid ""
"Fabric maintains two sets of API documentation, autogenerated from the "
"source code's docstrings (which are typically very thorough.)"
msgstr ""
"Fabric 维护了两套根据代码中 docstring 自动生成的 API 文档（它们都十分详尽）。"

#: ../index.rst:50
msgid "Core API"
msgstr "核心 API"

#: ../index.rst:52
msgid ""
"The **core** API is loosely defined as those functions, classes and methods "
"which form the basic building blocks of Fabric (such as "
"`~fabric.operations.run` and `~fabric.operations.sudo`) upon which "
"everything else (the below \"contrib\" section, and user fabfiles) builds."
msgstr ""
"**核心** API 是指构成 Fabric 基础构建块的函数、类和方法（例如 `~fabric.operations.run` "
"和 `~fabric.operations.sudo` ）。而其他部分（下文的“扩展 API”和用户的 fabfile）"
"都是在这些核心 API 的基础之上构建的。"

#: ../index.rst:66
msgid "Contrib API"
msgstr "扩展 API"

#: ../index.rst:68
msgid ""
"Fabric's **contrib** package contains commonly useful tools (often merged in"
" from user fabfiles) for tasks such as user I/O, modifying remote files, and"
" so forth. While the core API is likely to remain small and relatively "
"unchanged over time, this contrib section will grow and evolve (while trying"
" to remain backwards-compatible) as more use-cases are solved and added."
msgstr ""
"Fabric 的 **扩展包** 包括常用而有用的工具（通常是从用户的 fabfile 中合并进来的），"
"可用于用户 I/O、修改远程文件等任务中。核心 API 倾向于保持小巧、不随意变更，"
"扩展包则会随着更多的用户案例被解决并添加进来，而不断成长进化（同时尽量保持向后兼容）。"

#: ../index.rst:82
msgid "Contributing & Running Tests"
msgstr "参与 & 测试"

#: ../index.rst:84
msgid ""
"For advanced users & developers looking to help fix bugs or add new "
"features."
msgstr ""
"我们欢迎高级用户 & 开发者提交并帮助修复 bug，或者帮助开发新功能。"
